                <p>This version uses a promise chain to serialize updates to the shared <code>progress</code> variable. By ensuring that each update waits for the previous one to complete (via a queue of promises), we eliminate race conditions. Now, updates are applied sequentially, preventing skipped values or overruns. The progress is also capped at 100% for realism.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
